com.clapi.client

Class CLApiClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.clapi.client.CLApiClient

  • public class CLApiClient
extends Object
    Client to connect with connectlife server. 

      
 CLApiClient client = new CLApiClient("127.0.0.1", 9008, notification_listner);
 m_logger.debug( i + ": Connect - server version : " + client.getVersion() );
 if (client.checkCompatibility()) {
     client.getJsonData();
 }
    Author:
    ericpinet
    2015-11-05

    • Field Detail

      • API_CLIENT_VERSION

        public static final int[] API_CLIENT_VERSION
        Api client version. To check compatibility the difference with the first and third digit must be the same whit the client version. Exemple : Server version 0,1,2 : 0 - 2 = -2 Client version 1,1,3 : 1 - 3 = -2 Client and Server are compatible.
